snippet.title: Colour Fun- Yasho names colours in English and in Hindi | Kids learning game | Primary Colours
snippet.description:
Yasho learnt about colours through many fun activities. Children begin to learn colours during their preschool years and their ability to identify colours is considered a milestone in their cognitive development. Being able to distinguish colours helps build the cognitive pathways between visual clues and words. Therefore, engaging with children in helping them learn colours is essential.

In this game Yasho identifies basic colours and names and names an object of the same colour.
